1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,539
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:38,020
Episode 26

3
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:15,330
Mr. Li.

4
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:18,130
What on earth will you do?

5
00:02:19,260 --> 00:02:20,410
Commander Cao.

6
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:22,650
I just wonder

7
00:02:22,660 --> 00:02:24,450
about your health condition.

8
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:26,900
I know some famous doctors in Nanking.

9
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:27,970
They can...

10
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:30,610
Don’t beat around the bush.

11
00:02:30,780 --> 00:02:32,410
Come to the point.

12
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:35,450
I’ll say it straightly.

13
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:39,530
I think you are old and weak.

14
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,530
You can’t control the army.

15
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:43,130
Why don’t you hand over your military power?

16
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:45,450
I promise you’ll be a high-ranking official.

17
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:47,090
You think?

18
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,970
Who do you think you are?

19
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:50,730
Cao Wanjun.

20
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,130
I am good enough to you

21
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:55,130
since I don’t dismiss you.

22
00:02:57,540 --> 00:03:00,250
Don’t you know what you did?

23
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:01,730
I don’t know.

24
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:04,610
Commissioner Liu has known

25
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:07,210
what you asked Cheng Fengtai to do.

26
00:03:08,220 --> 00:03:10,050
Colluding bandits secretly.

27
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,210
How will others

28
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:13,130
see us soldiers if they know?

29
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:15,410
How angry will Mr. Jiang be

30
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:17,610
if he knows?

31
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,530
Prat.

32
00:03:27,420 --> 00:03:30,770
How come you hurt me with others?

33
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:33,130
In my heart,

34
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:35,410
the country is more important than the family.

35
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:37,090
So our relationship means nothing.

36
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:39,010
You are not young,

37
00:03:39,020 --> 00:03:40,770
so you can’t fight the battle at the front

38
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:43,410
physically and mentally.

39
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:44,570
Don’t forget.

40
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:45,970
Your surname is Cao.

41
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:47,410
You are my son.

42
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,810
We both are from Family Cao,

43
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:50,210
and we both control Cao’s army.

44
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:52,930
I am young.

45
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:56,090
Don’t you think I’m the right one to take over your army?

46
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,650
I can kill you now!

47
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:02,690
Father kills son.

48
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,490
The son can’t complain.

49
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:07,290
But I am your only son.

50
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,650
You decide

51
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:11,090
my fate.

52
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:12,730
Do you think I daren’t?

53
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:14,290
Mr. Cao.

54
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:18,130
Keep the goodies within the family.

55
00:04:18,850 --> 00:04:20,890
Cao Guixiu is your son.

56
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:23,010
OK.

57
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,730
You are my son.

58
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:27,410
How

59
00:04:28,220 --> 00:04:29,170
cruel you are.

60
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,170
I have nothing to say.

61
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:38,850
Commander Cao,

62
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:44,850
you did a lot for this country.

63
00:04:45,180 --> 00:04:47,170
It’s time to have a rest.

64
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:57,330
I’ll wait for you in Nanking.

65
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:04,970
See you in Nanking.

66
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:06,850
Commander Cao.

67
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,810
Take Cao’s army

68
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:22,050
and leave Peking.

69
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,370
Follow my order.

70
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,050
Yes.

71
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:34,690
You drank a lot.

72
00:05:37,180 --> 00:05:38,450
When we were at table,

73
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:40,810
your eyes were fixed on Chang Zhixin

74
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:42,130
and kept drinking.

75
00:05:43,940 --> 00:05:45,850
When will you move on?

76
00:05:45,860 --> 00:05:46,690
Tell me.

77
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,330
I’ll show Commander Cao out.

78
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:00,050
Go back to eat something.

79
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,570
Don’t make a mess.

80
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:02,770
I know.

81
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:13,170
He fixed his eyes on me.

82
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:17,650
Without Cheng Fengtai,

83
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:23,490
he would kick the table over.

84
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:25,890
That’s too exaggerating.

85
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:28,290
I don’t think he would.

86
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,290
Commander Cao and

87
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,650
Commissioner Liu are here.

88
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:32,770
How dare he?

89
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:35,130
Mr. Shang is not that kind of person.

90
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:36,970
You are wrong.

91
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:41,650
Cheng Fengtai is a good man.

92
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:46,890
But I don’t understand.

93
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:49,330
Why he makes friends

94
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:52,890
with Shang Xirui.

95
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:56,490
Does Shang Xirui deserve?

96
00:06:57,260 --> 00:06:59,570
He’s only good at performing opera.

97
00:07:00,020 --> 00:07:04,050
He’s notorious when it comes to other things.

98
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:07,330
With a bad temper,

99
00:07:07,940 --> 00:07:10,970
he will make troubles

100
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:15,130
in the future.

101
00:07:16,620 --> 00:07:17,890
Cheng Fengtai

102
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:20,690
will be involved in his matter.

103
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,250
I tell you.

104
00:07:24,140 --> 00:07:27,730
Tell your sister-in-law

105
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:31,570
not to bring troubles to himself.

106
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:33,530
OK.

107
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:35,010
Zhixin.

108
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:39,490
Mr. Shang.

109
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:42,090
Mr. Shang.

110
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:44,810
Zhixin.

111
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:47,290
We just had a casual talk.

112
00:07:48,420 --> 00:07:49,890
Don’t be serious.

113
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:51,450
Mr. Shang.

114
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:57,250
You took Jiang Mengping away several years ago.

115
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:01,090
Now, you make mischief between Cheng Fengtai and me.

116
00:08:01,260 --> 00:08:02,650
No, no, no.

117
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:03,610
We are drunk.

118
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:05,050
I’m not making mischief.

119
00:08:06,890 --> 00:08:12,530
What I said is the truth.

120
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:15,450
I’m not afraid that you know.

121
00:08:19,150 --> 00:08:20,570
Mr. Shang. Mr. Shang. No.

122
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:21,010
Stop.

123
00:08:23,610 --> 00:08:24,670
Who dares hit our leader?

124
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,730
Mr. Shang, Mr. Shang, please stop.

125
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:26,970
Mr. Shang, Mr. Shang.

126
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:28,850
Mr. Shang.

127
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:29,490
-Stop.
-Stop.

128
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:30,050
You can’t hit him.

129
00:08:32,049 --> 00:08:32,770
Mr. Shang.

130
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:34,210
Mr. Shang, Mr. Shang. Please stop.

131
00:08:34,690 --> 00:08:35,799
Please be sober.

132
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:36,409
Don’t go.

133
00:08:37,570 --> 00:08:38,890
I’m sorry, everybody.

134
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:40,210
Mr. Shang is drunk.

135
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,039
Chang Zhixin, I’ll kill you.

136
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:43,530
Go.

137
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,250
OK, OK, have a seat.

138
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,210
Sit.

139
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:50,850
Sit.

140
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:53,250
Zhixin. Zhixin.

141
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,170
Zhixin.

142
00:08:58,540 --> 00:08:59,850
Alright, have a seat.

143
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:01,090
Be seated.

144
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:02,730
Just continue.

145
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:04,330
Enjoy your dinner.

146
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:06,650
Zhixin, Zhixin. Are you all right?

147
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:07,370
Zhixin.

148
00:09:08,660 --> 00:09:09,370
Zhixin.

149
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:11,810
Zhixin.

150
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,330
Mr. Ge. Open the door.

151
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:25,810
Sweet potatoes with chestnut floor.

152
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:26,810
What happened?

153
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:30,690
Get in. Get in.

154
00:09:31,580 --> 00:09:33,930
Tomatoes on stick.

155
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:38,130
Tomatoes on sticks.

156
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:40,930
How dare you kick me?

157
00:09:40,940 --> 00:09:41,890
So what?

158
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:43,530
Could you stop being crazy?

159
00:09:43,540 --> 00:09:44,810
Let’s have a talk.

160
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,570
I’ll kill you.

161
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:51,730
Kill this jerk.

162
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:52,650
Mr. Shang.

163
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,610
What... What Chang Zhixin

164
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:54,490
did to you?

165
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:56,210
It’s been many years.

166
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:57,850
Can you move on?

167
00:09:59,940 --> 00:10:02,290
Cheng Fengtai, I am your friend.

168
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:03,410
But you stopped me beating him.

169
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:05,090
I’ll beat you!

170
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:12,210
Go away!

171
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:13,810
Ge. Go to Shuiyun Theater.

172
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:28,770
Stop.

173
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:32,570
Stop.

174
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:34,690
Mr. Cheng.

175
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:35,810
Move.

176
00:10:36,380 --> 00:10:37,690
Shang Xirui.

177
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:38,440
Come out.

178
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:40,130
Let’s have a fight.

179
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:43,290
Come on. You’ll be defeated.

180
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:48,970
-Mr. Cheng. Mr. Cheng.
-Dog. Dog. Dog.

181
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:54,860
Two kids.

182
00:10:57,610 --> 00:10:59,370
-What’s the matter?
-Mr. Cheng. Dog.

183
00:10:59,380 --> 00:11:00,090
Mr. Cheng.

184
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:00,810
Dog.

185
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,610
Mr. Cheng. Mr. Cheng. Mr. Cheng.

186
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:04,410
Hurry. Hurry.

187
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:05,370
Have a look.

188
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:07,370
Leader.

189
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:08,610
Mr. Cheng. What happened to our leader?

190
00:11:08,780 --> 00:11:10,090
-Leader. Leader.
-Mr. Cheng.

191
00:11:13,540 --> 00:11:14,250
No, it...

192
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:15,450
Leader. Leader.

193
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:16,970
What happened?

194
00:11:22,620 --> 00:11:24,090
Mr. Shang. Please stop.

195
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,690
I’ll die if you continue.

196
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,610
What are you shouting for? Did I hit you?

197
00:11:29,950 --> 00:11:30,930
Didn’t you?

198
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:34,230
What’s the teeth print?

199
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:35,810
From a dog.

200
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:38,010
God.

201
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:39,770
It’s black and blue.

202
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:44,410
Here. Here. It’s blue.

203
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:45,490
I wasn’t serious.

204
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:46,730
If I am,

205
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:47,530
killing you

206
00:11:47,540 --> 00:11:49,010
is a piece of cake.

207
00:11:51,940 --> 00:11:53,290
Chang Zhixin is my enemy.

208
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,690
Don’t be close to him.

209
00:11:54,940 --> 00:11:56,850
You didn’t even see Mengping.

210
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:58,850
How come you got crazy?

211
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,970
You can’t move on what happened

212
00:12:02,940 --> 00:12:04,650
on Pingyang for your life?

213
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:08,650
That’s not the reason.

214
00:12:08,660 --> 00:12:09,770
So what’s that?

215
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,570
Cut your crap. Come.

216
00:12:13,780 --> 00:12:15,130
Why? I don’t.

217
00:12:15,140 --> 00:12:15,890
Come!

218
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:17,370
No.

219
00:12:19,020 --> 00:12:20,300
(Miracle Vulnerary)

220
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:22,650
Have a try.

221
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:24,890
A miracle vulnerary of Shuiyun.

222
00:12:26,940 --> 00:12:31,100
(Cheng Mansion)

223
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:37,650
Stand straightly.

224
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:42,730
You become taller.

225
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:45,890
Xiang’er.

226
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:50,890
You are here?

227
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,210
Chacha’er has grown up.

228
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:58,770
So you can’t

229
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:01,170
always stay with me.

230
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,530
I’ll play with my nephew.

231
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,370
Xiang’er. Bye.

232
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:13,370
It’s a good choice to send her to school.

233
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:16,450
It’s beneficial for kids to grow up

234
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,850
if they go out.

235
00:13:18,580 --> 00:13:20,090
How was your feast last night?

236
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:21,650
Did everything go well?

237
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:24,630
Very well.

238
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,110
After hearing

239
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,190
Shuiyun Theater’s opera,

240
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,630
Liu Hanyun was very happy.

241
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,790
He shook hands with Commander Cao.

242
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:32,150
He didn’t even want to loose hands.

243
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,630
They were so close.

244
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,190
Really?

245
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,990
What did they play?

246
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,390
Like

247
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:40,350
White Snake.

248
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:42,110
Liu Hanyun liked it very much.

249
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,510
When they finished,

250
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,790
it was 3 a.m.

251
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,990
I was afraid

252
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,870
of bothering you.

253
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,870
So I slept at the hotel last night.

254
00:14:00,180 --> 00:14:01,590
Chacha’er didn’t take the fruits.

255
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,670
I’ll send to her.

256
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:21,430
These

257
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:23,230
are for you.

258
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:30,150
You think of me now?

259
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:32,350
It’s too late.

260
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:38,870
I don’t want gold.

261
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,470
I want diamond necklaces.

262
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,590
Under such a state,

263
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,670
diamond necklaces and cash

264
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,950
are useless.

265
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:52,230
Only gold talks.

266
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,750
Take these to protect yourself.

267
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,350
What do you mean?

268
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:03,230
I’m leaving for Nanking soon.

269
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:06,430
I just received the massage.

270
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,790
I’ll go in several days.

271
00:15:08,680 --> 00:15:11,590
Go back to your family with the gold.

272
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,270
It’s just Nanking.

273
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:14,790
It’s not far.

274
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:17,470
I’ll go to see you once I miss you.

275
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:20,150
After I go to Nanking,

276
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,410
it’s not easy for us to meet again.

277
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,510
Take these.

278
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:29,910
I’ll go with you.

279
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:34,630
I don’t go for having fun.

280
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,110
I lost my military power.

281
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:40,310
Seems that I’m promoted, but in fact, I am demoted.

282
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,830
I fear that our good days

283
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:45,390
are numbered.

284
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,350
I don’t care.

285
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,390
I’ll go with you even if I would suffer.

286
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:53,870
I also want you to go.

287
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:55,870
But you can’t go

288
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,950
to the place where I go.

289
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,510
I can’t?

290
