00:33:59,580 --> 00:34:00,970
I wouldn’t have learned opera

583
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:03,090
if I don’t need to earn a living.

584
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:05,450
Then learn to play Erhu and drum.

585
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,610
You can also learn to play the gong.

586
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:07,490
Except opera...

587
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:08,600
I want to leave this circle

588
00:34:08,610 --> 00:34:09,770
forever!

589
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,250
I don’t want to be beaten

590
00:34:11,719 --> 00:34:13,850
or looked down on by others.

591
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:17,870
Every hit that you get

592
00:34:18,230 --> 00:34:19,429
can make you a star!

593
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:21,870
With your ability,

594
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,550
your future is promising.

595
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:24,659
With Liu Hanyun,

596
00:34:24,670 --> 00:34:25,429
your prospect will totally

597
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,510
depend on him.

598
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:29,310
The men with power aren’t reliable!

599
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:36,070
Thousands of people sing opera in Peking,

600
00:34:36,080 --> 00:34:37,389
but few of them are stars.

601
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,179
Also,

602
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:40,550
even if I become a star,

603
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,510
I am just an entertainer.

604
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:44,179
I don’t want such a life anymore!

605
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,139
I want to be respected!

606
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:48,750
I want to be an official!

607
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:01,950
Alright.

608
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:05,390
Everyone has his own fate.

609
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,230
Since you’ve made up your mind,

610
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:10,230
I won’t persuade you.

611
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:13,230
Do as you please.

612
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,550
I’ll repeat the words.

613
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:20,750
From now on,

614
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:22,750
don’t step in Shuiyun Theater

615
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,110
no matter what life you’ll live.

616
00:35:37,200 --> 00:35:38,830
Thank you, leader.

617
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,230
Leader.

618
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:55,870
It’s more than 9.

619
00:36:56,240 --> 00:36:57,230
Get up.

620
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:00,910
Get up, leader.

621
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:02,030
This morning,

622
00:37:02,040 --> 00:37:04,990
I bought pea cake and beef with sauce for you.

623
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:07,270
Get up.

624
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:12,390
Don’t you eat?

625
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,350
I’ll give them to others.

626
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:15,830
Don’t.

627
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,430
Wash you face and brush your teeth.

628
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:17,930
Hurry.

629
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,790
Take care.

630
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:37,910
Excuse me.

631
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:40,150
Is Mr. Shang Xirui here?

632
00:37:44,440 --> 00:37:45,230
What happened?

633
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,070
Zhouzi.

634
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:48,270
Our leader is inside.

635
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,230
Follow me.

636
00:37:49,240 --> 00:37:49,850
What happened?

637
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,150
Take care.

638
00:37:53,760 --> 00:37:55,110
-Is he okay?
-What happened?

639
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,070
Leader!

640
00:37:56,150 --> 00:37:56,840
Leader!

641
00:37:56,870 --> 00:37:58,870
Leader!

642
00:37:58,960 --> 00:38:00,480
-Leader!
-Come out!

643
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:02,150
Leader! Come out. Leader.

644
00:38:02,160 --> 00:38:03,710
What are you shouting?

645
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,830
Leader. Come to see Zhouzi.

646
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:07,710
-He’s seriously hurt.
-Leader.

647
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:08,950
-Leader.
-Come.

648
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:10,790
Under the order of Commissioner Liu,

649
00:38:11,120 --> 00:38:13,550
I send him to you.

650
00:38:17,770 --> 00:38:18,590
Mr. Shang.

651
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:21,560
Zhouzi.

652
00:38:21,570 --> 00:38:22,610
Finally you are back.

653
00:38:22,620 --> 00:38:23,270
Mr. Shang.

654
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,090
Come on. Stand up.

655
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:24,640
Thank you.

656
00:38:24,650 --> 00:38:26,510
Stand up. Take him inside.

657
00:38:28,330 --> 00:38:29,250
Xiao Lai. Ask a doctor here.

658
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:35,270
Where is Mr. Liu now?

659
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,870
I need to thank him personally.

660
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:37,770
He was called back urgently.

661
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:40,130
So he went back to Nanking

662
00:38:40,580 --> 00:38:41,290
with Layue Hong.

663
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:52,930
Yes.

664
00:38:59,020 --> 00:38:59,490
Fengtai.

665
00:39:00,780 --> 00:39:01,730
-Mengping.
-What brings you by?

666
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:02,930
It’s heavy.

667
00:39:02,980 --> 00:39:03,730
Let me do it.

668
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:07,010
I come to visit Zhixin.

669
00:39:09,340 --> 00:39:10,090
He’s inside.

670
00:39:15,460 --> 00:39:16,890
Zhixin, are you better?

671
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:19,690
Fengtai.

672
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:22,290
I’m sorry

673
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:23,850
to make you come.

674
00:39:26,620 --> 00:39:27,890
I’m really sorry.

675
00:39:28,940 --> 00:39:30,370
I didn’t watch him.

676
00:39:33,060 --> 00:39:34,090
How come he still

677
00:39:34,660 --> 00:39:36,410
can’t move on?

678
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:41,250
I didn’t cheat him on purpose.

679
00:39:41,780 --> 00:39:43,010
Even though he hates me,

680
00:39:43,420 --> 00:39:44,890
he made a mess

681
00:39:45,660 --> 00:39:47,050
at the last meeting.

682
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:50,250
He shouldn’t have hit Zhixin this time.

683
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:55,150
Mengping, it’s not your fault.

684
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:58,410
He’s

685
00:39:58,700 --> 00:40:00,330
always like a kid.

686
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:03,370
If he doesn’t change his temper,

687
00:40:04,020 --> 00:40:05,370
what if he meets a tough issue

688
00:40:06,340 --> 00:40:07,530
one day?

689
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:16,930
Have a chat.

690
00:40:17,340 --> 00:40:19,650
I’ll prepare some tea for you.

691
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:28,090
Fengtai.

692
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:30,930
Tell me the truth.

693
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:34,170
Did you promise Shag Xirui something?

694
00:40:34,700 --> 00:40:35,530
Promise?

695
00:40:38,860 --> 00:40:40,650
I promised to buy him a theater

696
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:43,570
and take care of his account.

697
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:45,050
Did you realize them?

698
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,730
Yes.

699
00:40:46,950 --> 00:40:48,170
Anything else?

700
00:40:48,430 --> 00:40:49,290
Anything else?

701
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:56,770
A weird question.

702
00:41:00,540 --> 00:41:01,970
Mengping was here,

703
00:41:02,620 --> 00:41:04,050
so I didn’t say it.

704
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:06,210
Shang Xirui hit me

705
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:08,970
not because of Mengping,

706
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:11,210
but you.

707
00:41:12,500 --> 00:41:13,770
Because of me?

708
00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:16,130
Why?

709
00:41:17,020 --> 00:41:18,810
I said he doesn’t deserve to be your friend

710
00:41:21,620 --> 00:41:23,250
and want you to stay away from him.

711
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:25,730
He heard my words.

712
00:41:31,060 --> 00:41:32,230
I thought

713
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:35,250
after the matter of Pingyang,

714
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:38,890
he won’t believe anyone.

715
00:41:41,530 --> 00:41:43,570
But he believes you now.

716
00:41:45,110 --> 00:41:47,090
I think Shang Xirui

717
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:53,450
has taken you as his family.

718
00:41:53,820 --> 00:41:54,690
Do you know?

719
00:42:04,060 --> 00:42:05,450
I know it now.

720
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:10,170
Gently.

721
00:42:10,420 --> 00:42:11,530
How can it work if I’m gentle?

722
00:42:12,140 --> 00:42:12,770
Yes.

723
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:14,290
This is a little hurt.

724
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:23,450
It will be okay, Zhouzi.

725
00:42:27,220 --> 00:42:28,010
Leader!

726
00:42:28,260 --> 00:42:29,090
Leader!

727
00:42:29,380 --> 00:42:30,050
Leader!

728
00:42:30,060 --> 00:42:31,170
What’s the fuss for?

729
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:34,090
I can’t read the newspaper,

730
00:42:34,220 --> 00:42:35,890
but I know your rumor is running high.

731
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:37,570
They say you are Jiulang’s illegitimate child.

732
00:42:37,660 --> 00:42:39,730
Jiulang came back to the stage for you.

733
00:42:40,420 --> 00:42:41,930
If Jiulang is my father,

734
00:42:41,940 --> 00:42:43,490
I’ll laugh even in my dream.

735
00:42:44,060 --> 00:42:44,690
Also,

736
00:42:44,980 --> 00:42:46,970
they say you were really in love with Yu Qing.

737
00:42:47,020 --> 00:42:48,650
But you’ve broken up,

738
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:50,530
so your cooperation can’t be shown.

739
00:42:50,740 --> 00:42:52,450
I was in love with Yu Qing?

740
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:54,130
Damn it.

741
00:42:55,460 --> 00:42:56,050
Leader.

742
00:42:56,300 --> 00:42:57,210
Let me do it.

743
00:42:57,260 --> 00:42:58,480
You use too much strength.

744
00:42:58,620 --> 00:43:00,050
His hurt will be more serious.

745
00:43:00,060 --> 00:43:01,010
OK. You do it.

746
00:43:01,620 --> 00:43:02,290
Mr. Shang.

747
00:43:02,600 --> 00:43:03,090
I’m fine.

748
00:43:03,210 --> 00:43:03,890
It doesn’t hurt.

749
00:43:04,380 --> 00:43:05,170
Stop lying.

750
00:43:05,180 --> 00:43:05,890
Don’t move.

751
00:43:08,970 --> 00:43:09,890
It’s a little painful.

752
00:43:10,580 --> 00:43:11,330
Mr. Yuan.

753
00:43:11,620 --> 00:43:13,290
You don’t look after your pregnant wife

754
00:43:13,300 --> 00:43:14,970
but come to Shuiyun Theater?
